0.detail:
<p>You wouldn’t want to conduct a confidential business meeting at this 
snazzy teppanyaki joint, or, for that matter, a smoochy first date. Sen 
Nin is, however, perfect for a fun night out with
  friends, &amp; children will love it. Diners sit at shared tables 
fitted with a large hotplate, which acts as a stage for well-rehearsed 
chefs to pull off their culinary stunts: flipping, tossing,
  flaming &amp; juggling steak, prawns</p>

2.name: Squaremeal Review of Sen Nin
2.detail:
<p align="center"><font color="#333333">You wouldn’t want to conduct a confidential business meeting at this 
snazzy teppanyaki joint, or, for that matter, a smoochy first date. Sen 
Nin is, however, perfect for a fun night out with
  friends, &amp; children will love it. Diners sit at shared tables 
fitted with a large hotplate, which acts as a stage for well-rehearsed 
chefs to pull off their culinary stunts: flipping, tossing,
  flaming &amp; juggling steak, prawns &amp; vegetables before your 
eyes. It’s certainly entertaining &amp; the food doesn’t suffer. We’d 
suggest avoiding starters &amp; the average puds, &amp;
  sticking to set menus (around £20 for your choice of meat or fish, 
veg, rice &amp; miso soup). Otherwise, bills can get out of control. 
Lunchtime set meals offer good value, too.
</font></p>

4.name: Bershka
4.address: 67 Boulevard Al Massira Al Khadra, Maarif 20250, Maroc
4.detail:
<p><b>Bershka </b>a été créée en 1998 comme une nouvelle marque de groupe <i>Inditex</i>,
 avec un nouveau format de magasin qui répond aux exigences d'un secteur
 jeune intéressé et très bien informé sur les nouvelles tendances. 
<b>Bershka </b>est présenté comme un point de référence avant-gardiste ce de 
plus en plus exigeant et, en deux ans seulement, a atteint 100 
établissements consolider son image de marque....</p>

1.name: The Guggenheim s YCC Party
1.description:
<p>On Thursday <b>the Guggenheim hosted their annual YCC&nbsp;Party</b> to celebrate 
the 20th Anniversary of the Young Collectors Council along with&nbsp;the 
acquisition of over <font color="#ff9933">140 </font>works to the museum's private collection. The 
evening kicked off with cocktails and a&nbsp;private dinner at <font color="#ff6633">The Wright 
restaurant</font>. </p>
